    .o-container.o-container--sm.c-block#contact
        .u-textCenter
            h2.c-headline--inText Get in touch
            hr.c-rule--short
            p.c-text Begin an affirmative strength-based collaboration to make real change. Write to me using the form below, or get in touch:

        .u-textCenter.u-marginT15
            p.c-text.u-colorBrand.u-marginB0 Email: 
                a.o-link(href='mailto:#{email}') #{email}
            p.c-text.u-colorBrand Call: 
                a.o-link(href='tel:#{phone}') #{phone}
            p.c-text.u-marginT15
                | If you&apos;re not ready, you can fill in your details to unlock a single-page PDF of three proven ways to make effective change today.
        
        //- form#js-contact-form.c-form.u-marginT15(method='POST', action='https://formspree.io/callumflack@gmail.com')
        form#js-contact-form.c-form.u-marginT15(method='POST', action='https://formspree.io/#{email}')
            #js-contact-flash-messages
            .c-form-group
                input.c-form-control(placeholder='First Name', name='first-name')
            .c-form-group
                input.c-form-control(placeholder='Your email address', name='email')
            .c-form-group
                textarea.c-form-control.c-form-control--textarea(placeholder='How can I help you?', name='message', rows='3')
            .c-form-group.u-textCenter.u-spaceT
                button.c-button.c-button--primary.u-size1of2(type='submit') Submit

